# create layout
- create empty solution with dotnet nwe sln -n <yourname>
- create web api with dotnet new webapi -n <yourname>
- create classlib with dotnet new classlib -n <yourname>.Application
- create classlib with dotnet new classlib -n <yourname>.Domain
- create classlib with dotnet new classlib -n <yourname>.Persistence

# add refference
- API add Application
- Application add domain and persistence
- skip Domain
- Persistence add domain


# update db 
- dotnet ef migrations add InitiaCreate -p Persistence -s API
- dotnet ef database update InitiaCreate -p Persistence -s API
- dotnet ef migrations  remove -p Persistence -s API